reviews.text: Reasonable price, delicious and sincere services are the reasons to visit this little restaurant. Congees are as like bowls of tasty soups and u would just obsessed with the gourmets here. I won't miss it if i bring expat frds to hv a simpke meal here.
The quality of the food becomes worst than before. The crispy donut wrapped by rice roll got wet and not crispy. The congee was so-so and the price was reasonable,comparing with other congee shops.
This is the congee shop just like old time 50 years ago. Same atmosphere but not too untidy.....Same taste and price is really cheap...$10 for plain congee and less th@n $30 with various ingredients
Traditional congee & noodle shop which offer healthy, tasty and wholesome food for great value like in the 70 & 80's, unlike many shops today. Truly recommended!

Good old fashion Hong Kong congee shop with out-of-date low prices. But similarly comes with cramped space and old-fashion Hong Hong clamor, especially during lunch hour. However, great taste and good value.
